e upper and lower case)\",\r\n    \"ERR_PWD_NT_MTCH\": \"Passwords do not match. Kindly enter again.\",\r\n    \"ERR_INV_EMAIL\": \"Please enter a valid Email Address.\",\r\n    \"ERR_INV_PHN_NO\": \"Please enter a valid Mobile Number.\",\r\n    \"ERR_PWD_NOT_MATCH\": \"Password cannot be the same as the last 5 passwords. Please re-enter new password.\",\r\n    \"ERR_PASS\": \"Password should be of 8 to 15 characters (where the minimum length is 8 characters and maximum length is 15 characters) which should comprise of at least one number, special character and letters( at least one upper and lower case)\",\r\n    \"ERR_PASS_INVALID\": \"Password does not meet the minimum standards. Password should be of 8 to 15 characters (where the minimum length is 8 characters and maximum length is 15 characters) which should comprise of at least one number, special character and letters(at least one upper and lower case)\",\r\n    \"ERR_OLD_PASS\": \"Please enter the old password.\",\r\n    \"ERR_NEW_PASS\": \"Please enter the new password.\",\r\n    \"ERR_RE_PASS\": \"Please enter the password in re-confirm new password.\",\r\n    \"ERR_OTP\": \"Invalid OTP\",\r\n    \"ERR_EXPIRY\": \"Your password has been expired. Kindly change your password.\",\r\n    \"ERR_PROV\": \"Invalid Provisional ID / GSTIN / UIN\",\r\n    \"ERR_USERNAME\": \"You are required to choose a New Username. Username should be of 8 to 15 characters, which should start with an alphabet, should comprise of alphabets and can contain numbers, special character (dot (.), underscore (_) or hyphen (-))\",\r\n    \"ERR_SEQ_ANS\": \"Enter valid Security Answer\",\r\n    \"ERR_DATE\": \"Invalid date format. Please enter valid date in format DD/MM/YYYY\",\r\n    \"ERR_CAPTCHA\": \"Enter valid letters shown in the image below\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_8000\": \"System error occurred. Please try after sometime.\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9010\": \"Username should be of 8 to 15 characters (where the minimum length is 8 characters and maximum length is 15 characters) which should start with an alphabet, can contain alphabets, numbers and special characters (dot [.] or underscore [_] or hyphen [-])\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9011\": \"Password should be of 8 to 15 characters (where the minimum length is 8 characters and maximum length is 15 characters) which should comprise of at least one number, special character and letters( at least one upper and lower case)\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9030\": \"The username entered matches the pattern of PAN. Kindly choose a different username\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9021\": \"Session expired. Kindly Login again.\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9009\": \"Username already exists. Kindly choose another username\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9008\": \"Provisional ID / GSTIN / UIN entered is already mapped to a username.  Kindly login with valid username.\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9000\": \"Enter valid Letters shown\",\r\n    \"ERR_AUTH_9002\": \"Invalid Username or Password. Please try again\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9003\": \"OTP is incorrect. Kindly enter again.\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9004\": \"Please enter a valid Username\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9007\": \"Username is invalid. Please enter a valid Username.\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9017\": \"Passwords do not match. Kindly enter again.\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9018\": \"Your answer to security question is incorrect. Please try again.\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9029\": \"Error in changing password\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9023\": \"Passwords do not match. Kindly re-enter the details\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9024\": \"Please enter the new password and re-confirm new password\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9014\": \"You have entered a wrong password for 3 consecutive times. Your account has been locked. Kindly access ‘Forgot Password’ link to reset your password\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9028\": \"The Provisional ID / GSTIN / UIN entered by you doesn’t exists as per our records. Please enter your valid Provisional ID / GSTIN / UIN\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9025\": \"Invalid Password.\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9026\": \"Old Password entered is incorrect\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9027\": \"Password cannot be the same as the last 5 passwords. Please re-enter new password.\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9031\": \"Username is not created. Kindly contact your jurisdictional tax office to obtain username and password.\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_10001\": \"No records Found\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9032\": \"The Provisional ID / GSTIN entered by you doesn’t exists as per our records. Please enter your valid Provisional ID / GSTIN / UIN\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9034\": \"Dear Taxpayer, your registration is cancelled or marked inactive due to activity noticed on GST System which necessitated reconciliation of returns and verification of business under Rule 21 A and hence your login is not allowed. If you have not applied for cancellation or are not  involved in such activities, you may contact your jurisdictional authority with appropriate details for necessary redressal.\",\r\n    \"ERR_DATE_MAND\": \"Date is mandatory\",\r\n    \"ERR_TAX_TYPE_MAND\": \"Type of Tax is mandatory\",\r\n    \"ERR_DISC_TYPE_MAND\": \"Type of Discrepancy is mandatory\",\r\n    \"ERR_AMOU_INVO_MAND\": \"Amount Involved is mandatory\",\r\n    \"ERR_SWEB_9036\": \"ERR_SWEB_9036\",\r\n    \"ERR_JURS_MSG\" : \"* Jurisdictional officer is not currently assigned to this ARN. Please contact your jurisdictional office for further assistance.\",\r\n\r\n    \"ERR_ENTER_SEAR_CRIT\": \"Please enter at least one search criteria\",\r\n    \"EM_SRS_FO_030_04\": \"‘From’ Date cannot be greater than ‘To’ Date\",\r\n    \"ERR_EM_SRS_FO_030_03\": \"Please select a state\",\r\n    \"ERR_HSN_CODE_NAME\": \"Please enter an HSN code or name\",\r\n    \"ERR_SAC_CODE_NAME\": \"Please enter service classification code or name\",\r\n    \"ERR_ENTER_FROM\": \"Please select a ‘From’ Date\",\r\n    \"ERR_ENTER_TO\": \"Please select a ‘To’ Date\",\r\n    \"ERR_VIEW_ANNUAL_BY_YEAR\": \" To view Annual Returns please select Financial Year\",\r\n    \"ERR_NO_EF